Package: gpmodels
Type: Package
Title: A Grammar of Prediction Models
Version: 0.4.0
Author: Karandeep Singh
Maintainer: Karandeep Singh <kdpsingh@umich.edu>
Description: This package provides a grammar for data preparation and 
    evaluation of fixed-origin and rolling-origin prediction models using
    data collected at irregular intervals.
